data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This 2017-built gem offers a seamless blend of style and functionality. Stepinside to find elegant tile flooring throughout, a beautifully upgraded kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a striking backsplash. Theliving room boasts brand-new, top-of-the-line carpeting, creating the perfect space for relaxation. Outside, your oasis awaits with a fullyenclosed covered patio, paver landscaping, and the added luxury of no rear neighbors, ensuring peace and privacy. Enjoy the convenienceof living in the prestigious Vail School District, with the community pool and park just a stone's throw away. This home also features a custom security door for peace of mind, a water softener system with reverse osmosis drinking water, and the added benefit of solar.
